Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:48.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾相信的一切都背叛了那迷惘的年輕靈魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:55.50,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,Ce a quoi elle se raccrochera en dernier recourt ce sera...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:54.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最後的依靠，將是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十七幕\N告白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我「希望」這詞語的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 不正是您嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有您的信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何沉默不語
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何您一言不發
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話已無法傳達給您了…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是想這麼說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這世上沒有偶然」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該早已告訴過您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一切都是必然」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海黛若不是知道你父親真實身份的證人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我身邊有何價值？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若不是蒙代戈之子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我非在Luna與你相識…不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始伯爵就…將我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我裝作與你偶遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微的利用了一下你的信任與有情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那種小玩意兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「怎麼會…」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一開始伯爵就…將我…」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊 說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:04:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您竟從一開始就設計了這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 伯爵不是一直在幫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直都關心著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與您共同渡過的日子竟然都是騙局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想沉浸在那天真的幻想之中…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:06:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我明知那天海黛將在議會揭露一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特地邀你去旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你至今為止真的幫了我很大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我由衷地感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決鬥吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真經典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武將之子必須固守形式…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間是明晨五時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布洛涅森林
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盔甲和劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾圖喬 你做我的證人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自始至終認真看好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝 我正式接受決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 明晨五時見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是停留在今時今日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我們的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須去見他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都不能取消嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿爾貝先生的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您讓我「自由地生活」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才苟延殘喘至今
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若…您失去生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也無法再活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巖窟王啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒…時辰還未到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗郎茲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗郎茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都那麼關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我總是…不聽你的話 自把自為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 弗郎茲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦擦鼻涕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！那不是正中他下懷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種決鬥 立即給我取消
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會當我的見證人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會生氣也是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這是我無論如何都必須去做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 伯爵一開始就打算殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白白去當他復仇的犧牲品也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗郎茲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他欺騙我 敷衍我誘我上鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以最卑鄙的手段愚弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的生活全盤打亂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不能原諒他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若伯爵曾是你母親的未婚夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你父親因為太過愛她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十五年前讓伯爵背上莫須有的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強奪了他的未婚妻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙代戈夫人來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是愛德蒙·唐泰斯本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想見您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這二十五年來 我沒有一刻忘記過您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道您無法原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次 只要一次就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我和身為愛德蒙的您對話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身體只留下他的軀殼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本人已不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話為何我從剛見到您那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就預感到您是愛德蒙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這冰冷的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此無法可想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙 您曾經思念的人已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我證明給您看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明晨五時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布洛涅森林恭候駕臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經晚了 弗郎茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論過去伯爵與父親直接發生過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事已無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和伯爵之間發生的事 已無可挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那麼恨我的話就趕快殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 竟玩弄了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝 不行 別去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來 阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今仍要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗郎茲 回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 剛才還在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太好了 那天起完全聯繫不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真的很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過弗郎茲回來得正是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗郎茲 你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是阿爾貝的生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才來找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 少迷糊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我為阿爾貝譜了一首曲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還沒完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不符合歐仁妮風格的浪漫曲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 真失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 明天在老地方咖啡館
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、你和阿爾貝開個派對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說有朋友的發表會什麼的 溜出來就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 能拜託你點事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給他寫了生日卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個年紀了又不好意思親手交給他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 年紀怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只有我看到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有點原因啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我走之後你再交給阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給他個驚喜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我繼續作曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天 下午三點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老地方咖啡館
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝你 來看望我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您平安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為紅方的勝利乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為白方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他是黑方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要打垮他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 根本不足為俱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劃破拂曉的劍刃之音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手持憤怒之劍 斬斷欺騙與虛偽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 巖窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十八幕\N決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然後期待
